<FIRST>u f BC-TheWeekAhead     09-15 0152</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-The Week Ahead,0178</SECOND>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are the major business events and economic events scheduled
for the coming week (some dates are tentative; times are EDT):
</TEXT>
<BYLINE>MONDAY, Sept. 18</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   
   WASHINGTON _ Senate considers appropriations bills.
</TEXT>
<BYLINE>TUESDAY, Sept. 19</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   
   WASHINGTON _ Commerce Department reports housing starts for
August.
   WASHINGTON _ Labor Department reports Consumer Price Index for
August.
   HIGHLAND PARK, Mich. _ Chrysler Corp. introduces its 1990 models.
</TEXT>
<BYLINE>WEDNESDAY, Sept. 20</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   
   WASHINGTON _ House takes up aviation security legislation.
   CAMARILLO, Calif. _ Launch date for private rocket that will
hoist emergency re-entry vehicle for astronauts on space station.
</TEXT>
